WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.800
Mother had the opposite thing of being miserable because she was treated now gathered from

00:00:06.800 --> 00:00:13.760
Flora as a skivvy and she had to use, I now gather, the outside loo even though there

00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:20.200
were inside, it's a huge house, inside loos which she cleaned, people didn't speak to

00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:27.480
her, she had to eat in the kitchen on her own apparently, etc. and no one conversed

00:00:27.480 --> 00:00:32.840
with her if that's the right phrase. And so in one sense apparently she was quite happy

00:00:32.840 --> 00:00:38.400
when the regulation came out, you're too close to Liverpool and this military target and

00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:46.280
sensitive area, go. So both Bertil and Fanny and my father, they still didn't know each

00:00:46.280 --> 00:00:53.880
other, were all sent to Hlangollen where they then met up. My mother got a job at the Hand

00:00:54.360 --> 00:01:01.600
as a chambermaid. She buckled down to it, it's as simple as that and from what I gathered

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:07.200
it, you know, whatever was needed even though she was certainly, most certainly not used

00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:14.080
to it. So how efficient she was, I do not know because she was certainly not used to

00:01:14.080 --> 00:01:16.440
that sort of work doing it at all.

